content: Hi I have seen a lot of threads about goldsvet and here is a short list of what you need to knowGoldsvet has been circulating for sale for a while now, the code can be found free at https://discordme.at/ifnullIncluding the downloads of the game files and opensource code. A version 9 difference ( which you do not actually need if you have 8.5 running smoothly ) V9 is a single shop version PHP updated from 7.3+ support to 8.1 Laravel version updated from 8 to 9 A demo :: https://betshop.me    username garage456 pass : Test123 for frontendDownload include casino core, public_html core, sql file and a short installation doc for ready servers.This does not negate the fact that you might need installation help, hosting etc Just ask the right questions about code version, php support and hosting requirements Or just use the free version if you have those readyThe free version already includes shops support and atms/terminalsThe paid version as a single shop light version has instructions of how to unlock those features for developers
